_sText:
Original Author: [D*H] ~ Kon$olE
Mapper: Silent Ricochet

A nice fun map remade from an older 1.6 version by  [D*H] ~ Kon$olE. This map was a  lot of fun to test with others and everyone seemed to like it. It comes with HDR and a nav file for bots.

Features:

-Well optimized for maximum performance
-Fully built cubemaps for optimal reflections on all models
-Stylish Designs and Buildings
-AFK Kill Button
-High Dynamic Range Lighting
-NAV file with info_node_climbs for bot ladder usage

Perfect for Deathmatch or some quick rounds of pure fun.
